      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves for this exciting project car! This vehicle is the perfect canvas for someone looking to restore a classic to its former glory. While it definitely needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it's priced affordably and ready for a dedicated owner to give it a second life!",
