    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade vehicle of unparalleled caliber. This specimen has been meticulously preserved, exhibiting a pristine aesthetic and mechanical integrity that rivals its original showroom state. Every surface reflects a commitment to excellence, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior appointments. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class.",
