    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This is a showroom-quality masterpiece, preserved in a climate-controlled environment and presented in absolute peak condition. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its deep factory luster with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains a time capsule; the premium upholstery is taut and supple, the carpets are spotless, and every electronic component functions with the crisp precision of a new vehicle. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, benefiting from a documented, no-expense-spared maintenance history that ensures a driving experience identical to the day it left the assembly line. From the mirror-finish engine bay to the pristine undercarriage, every detail has been scrutinized to meet the highest standards. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a truly exceptional, investment-grade vehicle.",
      "price": 46500.0,
